block content
  h1.text-primary M2Pattern
  p.lead M2Pattern is a web-based basic block creation software that lets you create your basic pattern blocks from measurements entered in the system. The main idea of the application is to speed up the process of generating a custom block using your measurements without having to manually draft it from  scratch yourself.  Each measurement is used to generate a basic pattern that you can download as an SVG file or print as a pdf. The SVG files can be manipulated after download using other CAD software such as Optitex, Photoshop and Illustrator to create your desired design. 
  
  br
