      .col-md-6
        .card.h-48
          h4.card-header Measuring
          .card-body
            p.card-text
              | There are seven basic measurements needed to create the skirt draft. Check out a description of the required measurements and how to take them for each basic skirt block.
          .card-footer
            a.btn.btn-primary(href='/measure') Learn More
