        .card.h-40
          h4.card-header BuiltIn
          .card-body
            p.card-text
              | The application has inbuilt basic measurements if you just need to create the basic blocks for the standard sizes 6 to 14. You do not need to create an account to use this feature.
          .card-footer
            a.btn.btn-primary(href='/pattern/skirts') Learn More
